---
layout: layouts/home.njk
title: Home
description: Home Page
eleventyImport:
  collections: ["posts"]
---

<div class="min-h-screen hero bg-base-200">
  <div class="text-center hero-content">
    <div class="max-w-md">
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold">Hello there!</h1>
      <p class="py-6">I'm George D. Crochiere, a Software Engineering Major at Clarkson University.</p>
      <p class="py-6">This site has some of my web projects from COMM 429. Take a look around!</p>
      <button class="btn btn-secondary" onclick="location.href='#blog'">Get Started</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="min-h-screen hero bg-base-700" id="blog">
  <div class="text-center hero-content">
    <div class="max-w-md">
        <div class="border mockup-browser bg-base-300">
        <div class="mockup-browser-toolbar">
            <div class="input">/workout-app</div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col justify-center max-w-screen-sm px-4 py-12 bg-base-200">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold">Dev Blogs</h2>
            <p>Blog posts relating to web development and software engineering!</p>

            <div class="mb-2 stat">
                <div class="stat-figure text-accent">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="inline-block w-8 h-8 stroke-current"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path></svg>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-title">Total Blogs</div>
                <div class="stat-value text-accent">{{ collections.posts.length }}</div>
            </div>

            <button class="btn btn-accent" onclick="location.href='/blog/'">See More!</button>

        </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="min-h-screen hero bg-base-200" id="workout_app">
  <div class="text-center hero-content">
    <div class="max-w-md">
        <div class="border mockup-browser bg-base-300">
        <div class="mockup-browser-toolbar">
            <div class="input">/workout-app</div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col justify-center max-w-screen-sm px-4 py-12 bg-base-200">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold">Workout Application</h2>
            <p>An app utilizing API calls to deliver information on different exercises.</p>

            <div class="mb-2 stat">
                <div class="stat-figure text-secondary">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="inline-block w-8 h-8 stroke-current"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path></svg>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-title">Different Exercises</div>
                <div class="stat-value text-secondary">{{ baseData.results.length }}</div>
            </div>

            <button class="btn btn-secondary" onclick="location.href='/workout-app/'">See More!</button>

        </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

